# Changelog

## 2026-03-22
- Upgrade TinaCMS from v2.9.5 to v3.6.3 and @tinacms/cli from v1.12.4 to v2.x
  - New features: half-width fields, fuzzy search, file history, improved date picker, better media manager
  - Security patches included
- Make footer background fully black (#000000 instead of #111111)
